**Boot Menu Options**
Graphical Install → GUI installer with mouse support ✓ RECOMMENDED Install → Text-based installer (keyboard only) Live (amd64) → Boots without installing — no persistence Live (forensics) → Forensics mode — does not auto-mount drives Advanced options → Expert install, rescue mode, etc.

